text: Milorad Dodik (; born 12 March 1959) is a Bosnian Serb politician. He is the Serb member of the Presidency of Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Republika Srpska Category:Members of the Presidency of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Chairmen of the Presidency of Bosnia and Herzegovina
